tagline: This is a Tic-Tac-Toe Bot for discord
body:
Tic-Tac-Toe in Discord

This is a Tic-Tac-Toe Bot for discord That I made for [my discord server](https://discord.gg/P2BrjMN) using [Discord.net] (https://github.com/discord-net/Discord.Net).

With this bot you can play Tic-Tac-Toe in discord with your friends and have fun,for more info on how to use the bot head over to **__[@Ding Dong](https://github.com/shaahinfaezi/Discord-DingDong)__**
